INSERT INTO `wp_postmeta` (`post_id`, `meta_key`, `meta_value`) VALUES (3372, 'feature-body', '<h4>CLEANER SPA WATER</h4>\n<p>Crystal clear spa water is essential to your soaking experience, which is why we have invested in innovations in filtration and water care that keep your Highlife® Collection NXT spa water clean with as little work as possible.</p>\n<ol>\n<li style="list-style-type: none;">\n<ol>\n<li style="list-style-type: none;">\n<ol>\n<li><strong>ACE<sup>®</sup> Salt Water Sanitizing System<br />\n</strong>The <a href="/product/spa-accessories/ace-salt-water-sanitizing-system/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">patented ACE system</a> uses a diamond electrode to automatically generate chlorine sanitizer and other powerful cleaners from salt and water. You’ll spend less time maintaining your spa water, and use fewer bottled products which helps your spa water last longer between changes. This Hot Spring exclusive is an option for all Highlife NXT Collection spa models.</li>\n<li>The EverFresh water care system is a popular water care system among Hot Spring owners. The powerful combination of the FreshWater® III CD ozone system, FreshWaterAg+ Silver Ion Cartridge and MPS non-chlorine shock keeps spa water sparkling clean with reduced levels of chlorine. The FreshWater III ozone system is an option for all Hot Spot spa models.</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ol>\n');
