INSERT INTO `wp_postmeta` (`post_id`, `meta_key`, `meta_value`) VALUES (1005821, 'feature-body', '<h4>CLEANER SPA WATER</h4>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li><strong>Everfresh® System with Plasma Ozone</strong>Our exclusive EverFresh® System is a more natural approach to water care that’s optional on every Hot Spring Highlife and NXT Spa we sell. The beauty of EverFresh is that it’s virtually chlorine free! Never again soak in water with overpowering odor, or harsh drying effects on your skin. EverFresh will make routine water care easier, and keep your spa water crystal clean for longer periods of time.<strong>EverFresh consists of two main components that work in harmony with your Hot Spring’s 100% filtration:</strong>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li><strong>The High Output Ozone System</strong> continuously injects millions of tiny, highly concentrated ozone bubbles in the water, neutralizing contaminants on contact. Unlike ozone systems that use a UV bulb that need to be replaced on a regular basis (at considerable expense); our system uses a plasma chip that requires virtually no maintenance.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<ol start="2">\r\n 	<li><strong>The FreshWater AG+ Silver Ion Cartridge</strong>. Combined with the plasma chip ozonator, the silver ion cartridge is installed in one of the spas’ filters. Silver ions are then continuously introduced into the spa water. You’ll add a pre-measured “pod” of <a href="https://www.olympichottubestore.com/category-s/1910.htm">SilkBalance Shock Gems</a> after each use, which “activates” the silver ions to inhibit the growth of bacteria, refreshing and brightening the water. Simply replace the cartridge every four months for on-going protection. Signing up for our<a href="https://www.olympichottubestore.com/hot-tub-cleaning-service-buy-online-on-sale-s/1836.htm"> EverCare™</a> Program makes this a breeze.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Silk Balance makes hot tub water feel like silk</strong>. Your skin will feel soft and young again after every soak. If you’ve tried other hot tubs, you’ll notice the difference immediately: It’s perfect for sensitive skin. There’s no smell; no feeling of sitting in a vat of chemicals that can dry out your skin. You have to feel it to believe it!<strong>You’ll smell only fresh, pure water.</strong><strong>You’ll enjoy the best water quality day after day.</strong>Our hot tub water is…simply better. We’ve made hot tub water care simple and easy. Adding Silk Balance once a week keeps spa water in perfect harmony — it looks better, smells better and feels better, creating the bathing experience you want for yourself and your family.<strong>Makes hot tub water care simple!</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n');
